             the prisoners Brother; who told him that he knew Elizabeth Turner in Mark Lane: could counterfeit her hand, and would draw a Power for his Brother the Prisoner to receive the Money; that a Note to that purpose directed to Conrade de Gols Esq; was wrote by the prisoner at the <placeName id="t17220907-46-crimeloc255">Great James Tavern Bishopsgate Street</placeName>
